Slots Bitmap Data Slot slotId           = _SUBSCRIBER_SUBS_BITMAP_STATE_SLOT_ID or 0 msg.sender       = address of IDAv1 account          = context.msgSender Slots Bitmap Data Slot stores the bitmap of the slots that are \"enabled\" for a subscriber.  This is used as an optimization to only get the data (index id's) for the slots that are \"enabled\".
